Meta_Tags.keywords: filo-tag, filo, technology, bluetooth-device, device, filo tag, how it works
Meta_Tags.description:
Attach it. Ring it. Find it.
Attach Filo to all your personal objects to find them through a very simple mobile app.

Blocks.title: The tiny smart key finder
Blocks.description: Find your keys by attaching the Filo Bluetooth key finder to your keys and find them with the Filo app on your phone by simply ringing them. Spend less time looking and more finding your keys thanks to Filo Bluetooth tracker.
